Detailed Description

cvmx_gpio_clk_synce#

A QLM can be configured as a clock source. The GPIO block can support up to two unique clocks to send out any GPIO pin as configured by GPIO_BIT_CFG()[SYNCE_SEL]. The clock can be divided by 20, 40, 80 or 160 of the selected RX lane clock.
